subject: ARE YOU OKAY?!?!?!
body:
I heard from Dianne, you know her,
the nice lady with the two dogs across the street from your building,
that there had been some robberies in the area. Are you okay?
they didn’t steal anything from you did they? I think you should move,
you know I don’t like you living in that area of town.

Please email me back ASAP.
